  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/8ed3a0e086d8fe932e1342f55f873019.avif?t=1716900673\" width=601 height=208 /></span><br><br><strong>Toytopia</strong> is a first person 3D horror survival adventure game that takes place in a abandoned amusing children's attraction.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survive the abandoned levels of the most happiest place on earth.</h2>Welcome to Toytopia, where childhood innocence clashes with bone-chilling horror! Uncover the sinister secrets lurking behind the cheerful facades of your favorite toys in this spine-tingling adventure. Explore the abandon ruins of Toytopia experience the wonders that were once seen at this once amusing attraction. Always check behind your back because something is always lurking near you, meet the varying cast members of Toytopia and try your best to survive. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/f4d69cf1ce23ec5dc8391282d7fe10bb.poster.avif?t=1716900673\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/f4d69cf1ce23ec5dc8391282d7fe10bb.webm?t=1716900673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/f4d69cf1ce23ec5dc8391282d7fe10bb.mp4?t=1716900673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/ccfe571936759a8794fff699dc8958a5.poster.avif?t=1716900673\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/ccfe571936759a8794fff699dc8958a5.webm?t=1716900673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/ccfe571936759a8794fff699dc8958a5.mp4?t=1716900673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Embark on a twisted journey through a whimsical toy store turned nightmarish playground. Face off against a legion of haunted mascots brought to life, each with their own demented personality and nightmarish abilities. Every step forward brings you closer to the heart of darkness and to uncover the secrets that lies in Toytopia.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the ruins of Toytopia, which once was a happy place.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/9e4deff07a281f80ec6d00e0ce9e5f37.poster.avif?t=1716900673\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/9e4deff07a281f80ec6d00e0ce9e5f37.webm?t=1716900673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/9e4deff07a281f80ec6d00e0ce9e5f37.mp4?t=1716900673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Each room with their own unique patterns and challenges.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/ac9181658ca500e8b87ee9e27e6e63d8.poster.avif?t=1716900673\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/ac9181658ca500e8b87ee9e27e6e63d8.webm?t=1716900673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/ac9181658ca500e8b87ee9e27e6e63d8.mp4?t=1716900673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock and uncover the mysteries that lies within.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/dba6620305252c0ce63fec80bef8c793.poster.avif?t=1716900673\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/dba6620305252c0ce63fec80bef8c793.webm?t=1716900673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/dba6620305252c0ce63fec80bef8c793.mp4?t=1716900673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve challenging puzzles, deadly platforms and much more.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/ef3c7ca7f819a3218ed8637bbcf94343.poster.avif?t=1716900673\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/ef3c7ca7f819a3218ed8637bbcf94343.webm?t=1716900673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/ef3c7ca7f819a3218ed8637bbcf94343.mp4?t=1716900673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover rooms that were once known to make any child happy!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/e4883e9078c0c83c5251de10c6c8f0ee.poster.avif?t=1716900673\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/e4883e9078c0c83c5251de10c6c8f0ee.webm?t=1716900673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/e4883e9078c0c83c5251de10c6c8f0ee.mp4?t=1716900673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Filled with threats lurking at every corner.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/1ee46d60f302635c925e997fea08d1bc.poster.avif?t=1716900673\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/1ee46d60f302635c925e997fea08d1bc.webm?t=1716900673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/1ee46d60f302635c925e997fea08d1bc.mp4?t=1716900673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Waiting for the right moment to attack, you always have to stay alerted!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/d079c3828208254cfd876619283ea604.poster.avif?t=1716900673\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/d079c3828208254cfd876619283ea604.webm?t=1716900673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573590/extras/d079c3828208254cfd876619283ea604.mp4?t=1716900673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Navigate through eerie aisles and solve mind-bending puzzles while eluding the grasp of these monstrous playthings. Unravel the mystery shrouding Toytopia's grim transformation and confront the malevolent force pulling the strings. Toytopia is your one-stop place for <i>happiness</i>.. and <i>terror.</i> Will you survive?",
